 Her birthday bash was an A-list extravaganza featuring a decorated private dining room at Summer Place, in Hyde Park, Johannesburg.Guests were treated to a ballerina parade as part of the festivities.Matheba was a confectionery dream in a delicious strapless Gert-Johan Coetzee tulle ball gown, with its sweet pink hue.The guest-list included Matheba s boyfriend AKA, Maps Maponyane, Nomzamo Mbatha, Basetsana Kumalo, Fikile Mbalula, Khanyi Dhlomo and Lorna Maseko. The perfect night. Wow! Monate twaaaaa!! Bonang tweeted after the party.